    "company": "Colonial First State",
    "component": "Adaptive Form",
    "question": "Hidden components of adaptive form are visible on AEM pages, but work fine when previewing the form separately. Issue started suddenly and is reproducible in all environments.",
    "answer": "The issue is due to missing client libraries in the page policy. Adding the necessary client libraries to the page policy resolves the issue. It is documented that these client libraries are required to be included in the page policy. The customer should verify if they have transitioned from iframe mode to non-iframe mode or if they have modified template settings for the page."
}

